OL,3,CDonaldson removed from Privy Council
OL,5,FJeffrey Donaldson has been removed
OL,6,Ffrom the Privy Council, it has been
OL,7,Fconfirmed.
OL,9,FFormer DUP leader Donaldson was last
OL,10,Fmonth convicted at Newry Crown Court
OL,11,Fof 18 sex offences, including one
OL,12,Fcount of rape, relating to abuse of
OL,13,Ftwo women when they were children.
OL,15,FIn a statement from the clerk of the
OL,16,FPrivy Council, it was confirmed that
OL,17,FDonaldson had asked for his name to be
OL,18,Fremoved from the list of members last
OL,19,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
