OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783720151
OL,3,CDonaldson removed from Privy Council
OL,5,FThe Privy Council is a body of senior
OL,6,Fadvisers to the King.
OL,8,FThe clerk said: "Now, therefore, by
OL,9,Fand with the advice of His Majesty's
OL,10,FPrivy Council, it is hereby ordered,
OL,11,Fthat the name of the said Jeffrey
OL,12,FDonaldson be removed from the list of
OL,13,FMembers of His Majesty's Most
OL,14,FHonourable Privy Council."
OL,16,FDonaldson has also moved to renounce
OL,17,Fhis knighthood ` a process which can
OL,18,Foccur through a recommendation of the
OL,19,FForfeiture Committee, convened under
OL,20,Fthe Cabinet Office.
OL,26,@pD@QOUvD@ZO]
