OL,3,CDonaldson removed from Privy Council
OL,5,FThe body's recommendations for
OL,6,Fforfeiture are submitted through the
OL,7,FPrime Minister to the King.
OL,9,FEarlier this week, the DUP revealed
OL,10,Fdetails of a "focused, independent
OL,11,Freview" commissioned to establish what
OL,12,Fwas known within the party about
OL,13,FDonaldson's conduct.
OL,15,FThe review will be led by Jim Gamble,
OL,16,Fa former RUC officer and head of the
OL,17,FChild Exploitation and Online
OL,18,FProtection Command (CEOP) Centre.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
